HEADWORD: Sublation
<hw>Sub*la"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>sublatio</ets>, fr. <ets>sublatus</ets>, used as p. p. of
<ets>tollere</ets> to take away.]</ety> <def>The act of taking or
